                    <span>Second only to the Bible itself, this book speaks directly to the heart and spirit of the Christian. It makes a great devotional, as it lends itself best to careful reflection, a little at a time. It demands to be reread as one matures as a Christian, always with fresh insight.</span>
                  
              
